{"tid":357074,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"干地嘲諷「避免摩連奴球季」車路士排第10名不可再發生","createTime":"2017-08-12T14:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T04:36:53.000Z","uid":120575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b30b2f7f76008f3b522f03e8d346d5ba3141cd3","tid":357074,"uid":120575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"干地口中的「摩連奴球季」，是指車路士2014/15球季在摩連奴率領下獲得英超冠軍，惟翌季表現大跌令摩帥季中被炒，最終以英超第10名完成2015/16球季。干地就指出：「車路士兩年前排第10名，那不可以再發生。」對上一支成功衛冕英超的球隊，已經是2008/09球季的曼聯，干地對此表示：「我們明白（衛冕）有多困難，當然我們要避免『摩連奴球季』。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">半場三比零</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又捉鬼了</span></span>"},{"pid":"ddb36176a26935684f3333f80a6d45418f12c8f1","tid":357074,"uid":120575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91039b81600623870b70cbf45c4924ddd1b2ba1","tid":357074,"uid":120575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0c79b7b109b2fc184586e476aa4fd30eedd030","tid":357074,"uid":58863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DHCWmMkXsAALJ-r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h